description:
Full course on Udemy: https://www.udemy.com/course/make-short-films-in-unreal-engine-5-with-metahumans/?referralCode=82159B94DE37A6676C3E

Discover the exciting world of filmmaking in Unreal Engine 5 with my brand new beginner-friendly course on creating short films using Unreal Engine 5 and Metahumans. Whether you're a new filmmaker or someone who has experience, this course will walk you through the process of bringing your stories to life in a stunning virtual environment. 

In this course, you'll learn step-by-step how to use Unreal Engine 5, a powerful and free-to-use software, to build your own cinematic worlds. We'll start by exploring the basics, like how to navigate the software and use its tools to create a whole natural environment set for your film. Then, we'll introduce you to Metahumans, a groundbreaking tool that lets you design realistic digital actors with ease. You'll learn how to customize characters' appearances, movements, and expressions, giving them a lifelike quality that enhances your storytelling. (We will use Metahuman Creator to create the characters and Metahuman Animator to animate the facial expressions).

We will also talk about how to plan your camera movements and make your film look as cinematic as possible.

By the end of this course, you'll have the skills and confidence to create your own short films using Unreal Engine 5 and Metahumans. Whether you want to share your stories with the world or simply explore the possibilities of digital filmmaking, this course will empower you to bring your creative vision to life like never before.
